SERVER AND TOOLS LICENSES PRODUCTS, APPLICATIONS, TOOLS, CONTENT, AND DELIVERS ENTERPRISE SERVICES, ALL OF WHICH ARE DESIGNED TO MAKE INFORMATION

TECHNOLOGY PROFESSIONALS, DEVELOPERS AND THEIR SYSTEMS MORE PRODUCTIVE AND EFFICIENT. SERVER AND TOOLS PRODUCT AND SERVICE OFFERINGS CONSIST OF WINDOWS SERVER, MICROSOFT SQL SERVER, WINDOWS AZURE

25

