QUERIES AND AN EXPANDED AND MORE COMPETITIVE SEARCH AND ADVERTISING MARKETPLACE. SEE NOTE 16  COMMITMENTS AND GUARANTEES IN THE NOTES TO FINANCIAL STATEMENTS (PART II, ITEM 8 OF

