FISCAL YEAR 2010 COMPARED WITH FISCAL YEAR 2009

OSD REVENUE INCREASED REFLECTING INCREASED ONLINE ADVERTISING REVENUE, OFFSET IN PART BY DECREASED ACCESS REVENUE. ONLINE ADVERTISING REVENUE

