ENTERTAINMENT AND DEVICES DIVISION (EDD) OFFERINGS INCLUDE THE XBOX 360 PLATFORM (WHICH INCLUDES THE XBOX 360 GAMING AND ENTERTAINMENT

CONSOLE, XBOX 360 VIDEO GAMES, XBOX LIVE, AND XBOX 360 ACCESSORIES), THE ZUNE DIGITAL MUSIC AND ENTERTAINMENT PLATFORM (ZUNE), PC SOFTWARE GAMES, ONLINE GAMES AND SERVICES, MEDIAROOM (OUR INTERNET PROTOCOL TELEVISION SOFTWARE), WINDOWS

PHONE AND WINDOWS EMBEDDED DEVICE PLATFORMS, APPLICATION SOFTWARE FOR APPLES MACINTOSH COMPUTERS, MICROSOFT PC HARDWARE PRODUCTS, AND OTHER DEVICES. EDD IS ALSO RESPONSIBLE FOR ALL RETAIL SALES AND MARKETING FOR MICROSOFT OFFICE AND WINDOWS

OPERATING SYSTEMS.

